(39828, 30903, 0, 1, '轉變', '', '2011-10-15 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 3, '臨座的妳 忽然變成 一張陌生的臉\r\n距離很近 卻不能 觸碰的肩\r\n妳捲曲的髮線 傳來 一陣陌生的香味\r\n忽遠 忽近 忽遠 忽近\r\n\r\n\r\noh my love 勇敢的花不害怕凋謝\r\noh my love 沒有什麼能永遠不變\r\n\r\nlet it be \r\n蒲公英 選擇分裂自己  \r\n然後孕育生命 然後孕育生命\r\n \r\n生命 生生不息\r\n\r\n\r\n昨天的事情 沒有人能夠改變\r\n有隻自由的鳥 在你 心裡飛\r\n\r\n沒人能選擇 究竟要不要往前\r\n只能看著世界 靜靜的轉變\r\n\r\njust let it be 勇敢的花不害怕凋謝\r\njust let it be 沒有什麼能永遠不變\r\n\r\n那冷冽的風 撫慰甘涸的大草原\r\n田中央 的狼煙 他向著誰\r\n \r\n\r\noh my love      勇敢的花不害怕凋謝\r\njust let it be  沒有什麼能永遠不變\r\n蒲公英 分裂自己 孕育著生命\r\n田中央 的狼煙 向著誰 向著誰 向著誰 向著誰\r\n\r\n蒲公英 分裂自己 孕育著生命\r\nlet it be 勇敢的花不害怕凋謝\r\noh my love 沒有什麼能永遠美艷\r\n\r\n看著世界 在你放手的時候  靜靜轉變', '', 288, '', '閻韋伶', '閻韋伶', '閻韋伶', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-10-15 15:44:16', '2015-03-12 13:48:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(39829, 123757, 0, 1, 'On No Words', 'The song "On No Words" from "LOVE I LOVE" was selected for the finalists from over 1600 songwriters from 45 countries around the world in the 12th Annual Great American Song Contest.\r\n\r\n\r\n" LOVE I LOVE" was produced by Malcolm Burn, a Grammy-award winning producer, who has worked with Bob Dylan, Daniel Lanois, Peter Gabriel, Emmylou Harris, etc.\r\nFU is the first band that Malcolm Burn produces in the sphere of Japan and Asia.\r\nIt is critically acclaimed in USA, Canada and Japan.\r\nRichard Hoak, the drummer of Brutal Truth selected "LOVE I LOVE" for best of 2010.\r\n\r\n" FU craft a lustrous, epic, major label-worthy record..."\r\n" FU run the gamut of Westernized modern rock, finding a proverbial\r\nconnection with the listener..." (exclaim! mag / Canada)\r\n\r\n" It’s not possible to really categorize the sound achieved by the band,\r\nworking with Grammy Award winning producer Malcolm Burn.\r\nThink Muse with invented language. Think about what Peter Gabriel \r\nmust hear inside his head before he records." (''Round Magazine / USA)\r\n\r\n" FU-A fantastic new Japanese band" (Malcolm Burn / Producer )\r\n', '2010-07-28 00:00:00', 2010, 0, 1, 7, 'On No Words', '', 235, '', 'Ubi Quitous', 'Ubi Quitous', 'Malcolm Burn', 'IZIGEN MUSIC', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-10-15 16:00:00', '2013-10-07 17:19:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
