(39849, 123837, 0, 1, 'Smiling moon(demo)', '在寂寞的夜裡其實我們並不寂寞', '2011-10-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '不見的星空 夜晚充滿這寂寞\r\n握緊的雙手 拋不開這宇宙\r\nIf you can touch me,I will give you all\r\nIf you can hear me,I will give you my soul\r\n\r\n所有你受的傷 回憶裡的痛苦 你不用再害怕\r\n有我陪著你\r\nSo you are not alone\r\n過去的一切 堅持著未來\r\n\r\n黑夜籠罩著 失溫的我不斷墬落\r\n是否在我的心中 還保留原來的我\r\nIf you can touch me,I will give you all\r\nIf you can hear me,I will give you my soul\r\n\r\n喔我知道很難 我想找個出口\r\nUtill I find it,I’m free in this world\r\n\r\nI want to leave this,try don’t be lonely\r\nAnd tell the world I find\r\nI got to do this and prove the word that\r\nI get the strength to fight\r\n', '', 326, '', 'Together', 'Together', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '2011-10-16 04:06:41', '2013-10-07 17:19:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
